{"tid":2086633,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"港共等唔切了","createTime":"2020-06-30T10:52:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-30T10:59:13.000Z","uid":93600,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"5d6969c2127b17f9a363744b16d2816357e8fcef","tid":2086633,"uid":93600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:52:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bqSU40w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbqSU40w.jpg&h=f4dfd9de&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"411666c934f0c9ac21a2ee69e1b8bf7f52ef363e","tid":2086633,"uid":60924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"12點就12點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天文台咁"},{"pid":"26fd465032ae70fcc2a50be28e064d6433c39d77","tid":2086633,"uid":34577,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"411666c934f0c9ac21a2ee69e1b8bf7f52ef363e","tid":2086633,"uid":60924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:53:35.000Z","msg":"12點就12點啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />天文台咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:56:17.000Z","msg":"預計會喺 12 點生效 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74280902ea5449bcf587ccef92a54915aa7bab06","tid":2086633,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:56:39.000Z","msg":"手足，大家聽日見，準備好道具比國際傳媒影啊<br />\n<br />\n今年七一要加主題：<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n寧願最後不得善終<br />\n也不考慮含淚折衷<br />\n<br />\n我要美國制裁，無懼與支共同歸於盡，寧死捍衛自由民主</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n認同就拎張紙舉<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">Thanks, Pompeo</span></span></strong>比美國睇，咪比條廢老Martin Lee騎劫我地，搞到美國以為我地驚攬炒而唔做野<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黃世澤出左香港自治法篤灰指南，好有用，大家入去睇</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n\t<br />\n\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fs6o2r5DkT-w&d=r9GgQvVcrWtMp%2Fshn5VX%2F7eFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=c8fcf33a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/s6o2r5DkT-w</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n正視聽：若抗爭方向不隨局勢改變，只會無謂地損兵折將<br />\n香港街頭抗爭目標，亦都係街頭抗爭最大效果；&ldquo;攬炒&rdquo;已經達到，今次搞蟈安法其實仲攬炒過上年出老解。<br />\n宜家<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">跟著落黎就係引導全球政府同議會（尤其美國）對付支那以及滅共</span></strong>，所以大家重點應該著眼帶出清晰民意授權比各國政府做野，畫面靚+全球廣泛報導（類似反蟈安法銅鑼灣自由行）係最理想，用選票帶出民意亦十分重要。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">大家要小心五毛、熱狗放負風向：美國唔會幫我地（舊年年尾）-》英國係廢國無用架（今年年頭）-》歐盟奶共唔會幫我地、美國廢架制裁無用（宜家）</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n大家要記住，香港生路只有一條：救香港人+攬炒促進支爆+重建香港。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">沒有支爆，香港獨立或者歸英等重建方案全部都係痴人說夢。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n未來幾個月至支共瓦解期間大家要做嘅事：1.<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">走資</span></strong>2.全球救生艇<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">救手足加有細路既黃絲家庭</span></strong>（細路是重點，香港未來棟樑，正如今時今日d前線義士，咪比佢地洗腦變小糞紅，否則香港係真正玩完）3.比足夠<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">民意授權，敦促美國以至各國凌遲式消除香港作為支那獲得外資渠道</span></strong>，包括但不限於：禁止美國個人或公司投資港股，暫停接受香港用美元結算等等4.最後就真係等<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>支那自己爆</strong></span>"},{"pid":"9068a10b702c68aa32c47488986ada0a69430685","tid":2086633,"uid":107212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T10:57:27.000Z","msg":"全港700萬人都未睇過啲條文就生效<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0134bf58d74e4170a16f1fdbb5f5242718b3e0eb","tid":2086633,"uid":93600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"411666c934f0c9ac21a2ee69e1b8bf7f52ef363e","tid":2086633,"uid":60924,"like":3,"di